long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
🚀 Effortlessly One-click find similar web based on your url or domain powered by AI, and easy export as Excel/CSV/JSON/HTML/XML file.

🔧 How it Works:
1️⃣ Click extension icon.
2️⃣ Click the "Search" button on extension popup.
3️⃣ Choose to download from the data scraping pop-up or the task list on extension.

✨ Included features:
1️⃣ You can find similar web by any url bobobor domain, that's powered by AI.
2️⃣ You can export data into Excel/CSV/JSON/HTML/XML, data include similar url, url title, similar score, publishDate.
3️⃣ You can manage your history scape task data.
4️⃣ Discover our more powerful tools.

💡 What can I used for:
1️⃣ Competitive Analysis 🔍: Effortlessly identify your competitors' online presence and stay ahead of the curve. Quickly scan for similar websites in your industry and gain valuable insights to enhance your digital strategy.
2️⃣ Content Inspiration 💡: Discover relevant websites with inspiring content. Leverage the AI-powered similarity search to expand your horizons and create unique, engaging material for your audience.
3️⃣ Influencer Outreach 🤝: Efficiently locate influential websites and bloggers in your niche. Use the one-click similarity search to identify potential partners for influencer marketing or guest posting.
4️⃣ Market Research 📊: Thoroughly investigate the online landscape of your target market. Uncover emerging trends, popular websites, and new players in your industry to empower your data-driven decisions.
